{"tid":578241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「開心大發視」原來宜家D錫紙係鋁紙黎","createTime":"2018-03-02T12:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T14:23:34.000Z","uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"60098a594144660df28863b06cf21f98c4c8cf94","tid":578241,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:41:20.000Z","msg":"其實有冇違反商品說明條例？？<br />\n<br />\n有好多研究都證實左鋁加紙好易釋出鋁入D食物度，長期食會壞腦架喎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/204113_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F204113_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=02307bb6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee419fb59ceaa14c6a7df147e97243574bae0c34","tid":578241,"uid":156363,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:44:02.000Z","msg":"錫紙燒烤暗藏鋁毒<br />\n長期攝取易腦退化損性能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】踏入秋季，便是郊遊燒烤旺季，許多人以為用錫紙包住食物燒烤，能阻止燒烤炭釋出的有害物質污染食物，但這做法卻暗藏鋁中毒危機。有生化系教授指出，錫紙包住食物加熱會釋出鋁，長期攝取會食壞腦，除了增加患腦退化的風險外，更影響性能力，勸喻市民減少用錫紙加熱食物。<br />\n記者：林賽香<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20121104/18057212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20121104%2F18057212&d=eY5UXxbvZ0WcAG%2BJmA8FFv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d991516c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20121104%2F18057212&h=6acd47e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20121104/18057212</a>"},{"pid":"14ff979f1f3165f20c761d4d570e335350da07d9","tid":578241,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:44:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a1db097e5103e0ee89debbedaad2b158fde63b9","tid":578241,"uid":8257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"60098a594144660df28863b06cf21f98c4c8cf94","tid":578241,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:41:20.000Z","msg":"其實有冇違反商品說明條例？？<br />\n<br />\n有好多研究都證實左鋁加紙好易釋出鋁入D食物度，長期食會壞腦架喎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/204113_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F204113_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=02307bb6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:46:46.000Z","msg":"英文字都寫左係鋁啦"},{"pid":"a29ba688e0867446a040cc6825195d5e1a41dc3f","tid":578241,"uid":79632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:46:55.000Z","msg":"以英文版為準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff70d3f49d1b734f7a79570cffcb99001ee21ce","tid":578241,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"8a1db097e5103e0ee89debbedaad2b158fde63b9","tid":578241,"uid":8257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"60098a594144660df28863b06cf21f98c4c8cf94","tid":578241,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:41:20.000Z","msg":"其實有冇違反商品說明條例？？<br />\n<br />\n有好多研究都證實左鋁加紙好易釋出鋁入D食物度，長期食會壞腦架喎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/204113_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F204113_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=02307bb6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:46:46.000Z","msg":"英文字都寫左係鋁啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:53:29.000Z","msg":"我一直都以為係錫黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />